, "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75388629_496686605807277_8073426984527104616_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=fZZiA9tzTkgQ7kNvgG23YRH&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AoEEQKrntbw-a0TV-oZZPd6&oh=00_AYCQ_7kzMLCexM4rpb6T2-WcIkUS9R7LStqfHzdd0lBJXw&oe=66E42A38"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Ovation_Trailer_Thumbnail.png", "id": "841855751114814", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982496_841855754448147_6704836506894212103_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=qRtwhJJee8MQ7kNvgEumKHd&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AoEEQKrntbw-a0TV-oZZPd6&oh=00_AYCi0KZY1A0duOQWUHrC78XRqC2NS3rYcssX3zhx8lHcdA&oe=66E427C9"}, "display_name": "Ovation", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Speak Confidently, from Virtual to Reality\n\nAre public speaking jitters holding you back?\nDo you aspire to captivate every room?\n\nWith Ovation, harness the power of VR and AI to practice, perfect, and perform when it matters most.\n\n*Subscription required for advanced features*\n\nRealistic Audiences & Venues\nAudience members are real people scanned into 3D models. An ever-expanding collection of venues includes conference halls, classrooms, and boardrooms.\n\nEndless Customization\nImport your text, slides, and slide notes. Choose from dozens of interactive speech tools.\n\nAI-Powered Speaking Scenarios\nOvation\u2018s simulated audience members can engage in intelligent dialogues powered by ChatGPT and ElevenLabs.\n\n\u2022 Speech + Q&A: Deliver your presentation then answer questions about it.\n\u2022 Conversation: Choose any topic and discuss it with simulated participants.\n\u2022 Interview: Prepare for any job interview in any industry. Alternatively, be the interviewer and evaluate AI applicants.\n\nReal-Time Training\nYour performance is evaluated as you speak, with notifications informing you the moment you say a filler word, stare at one side of the audience, and more.\n\nRecording & Playback\nPractice sessions are recorded in 3D, enabling you to watch your performance from every angle.\n\nAI-Powered Feedback & Analytics\nEach performance is evaluated by ChatGPT, providing insightful feedback to help you improve.\n\nMultiplayer\nMeet up with others virtually in Ovation, no matter where you are.\n\nAre you ready for your Ovation?", "short_description": "Speak Confidently, from Virtual to Reality\n\nAre public speaking jitters holding you back?\nDo you aspire to captivate every room?\n\nWith Ovation, harness the power of VR and AI to practice, perfect, and perform when it matters most.\n\n*Subscription required for advanced features*"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.ovationvr.com/VRSpeaking_PrivacyPolicy.pdf", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "VRSpeaking", "support_website_url": "https://www.ovationvr.com/contact", "website_url": "https://www.ovationvr.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1063584910766706"}, {"id": "421923165850360"}, {"id": "393222478507326"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": ["EDUCATIONAL", "PRODUCTIVITY", "SIMULATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER", "SINGLE_USER", "CO_OP"], "id": "7659916294046556"}, "review_messages": ["", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031346_1605428639898413_7499009506370406748_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc